atform Phase","quest_id":176000006},{"text":"\"No need to hurry, {PlayerName}. Rest here for a while. This view belongs to you too,\" says Dhalifa!","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Platform Phase","quest_id":176000006},{"text":"Dhalifa is back! Dhalifa is back!","quest_name":"Spacetrek Observatory: Overwatch Phase","quest_id":176000007}]}